    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion has softened, add your <strong>ground smoked paprika</strong>, <strong>ground</strong> <strong>cumin</strong>,<strong> tomato paste</strong>, <strong>chicken stock mix</strong> and<strong> drained sweetcorn </strong>with 50ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[75ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[100ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Cook for 2-3 min further, or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) and the sauce has slightly thickened – this is your <strong>chicken & sweetcorn filling</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
