    {
      "instruction": "<p>Divide the <strong>chicken & sweetcorn filling</strong> between your <strong>tortillas</strong></p><p>Roll each <strong>tortilla</strong> up and arrange them in an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong></p><p>Top with the <strong>enchiladas suizas sauce</strong> and <strong>grated</strong> <strong>cheese</strong></p><p>Put the dish in the oven and cook for 15-20 min or until the cheese has melted – these are your <strong>chicken thigh enchiladas suizas</strong></p>",
